Travoprost ophthalmic solution, USP (ionic buffered solution) contains

  Active:travoprost 0.04 mg/mL;

  Inactives:polyoxyl 40 hydrogenated castor oil, ionic buffered system (boric acid, propylene glycol, sorbitol, zinc chloride), sodium hydroxide and/or hydrochloric acid (to adjust pH), and water for injection. Preserved in the bottle with an ionic buffered system.
